                🔄 A2A
            </NavLink>
            <NavLink href="/demos/edge-iot" 
                     title="Edge IoT Predictive Maintenance Demo: Industrial IoT simulation with edge-cloud hybrid architecture. Simulate sensor data, detect anomalies, and generate maintenance work orders."
                     class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-green-500 font-medium">
                🏭 Edge IoT
            </NavLink>
